 to invest in it yet. The prices are high, and 8K content is limited. So, the best sweet spot is 4K, which offers a great middle ground.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"connectivity-options\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Connectivity options\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"here-more-is-better\"\u003e\n            Here, more is better\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/pxl_20241023_110041616-mp.jpg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source: Amazon\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/pxl_20241023_110041616-mp.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/pxl_20241023_110041616-mp.jpg?q=49\